Using [Java code], generate a random slogan for a software company that specializes in AI-based solutions.
Here is the code implementation to generate a random slogan:
import java.util.Random;
public class SloganGenerator {
  public static void main(String[] args) {
    String[] slogans = {"Empowering AI for a better future", "Innovative AI solutions for your business", "Experience AI like never before", "Revolutionizing the world with AI"};
    Random random = new Random();
    int index = random.nextInt(slogans.length);
    System.out.println(slogans[index]);
  }
} 
What other slogans can you suggest for the software company that specializes in AI-based solutions?
